Bootstrap 4 From Scratch With 5 Projects


Section 1: Intro & Getting Started (32min)

    7. Headings & Basic Typography
    - rem and em units: Are multipliers.
        - em goes by parent font size.
        - rem goes by html root font size.
        - class="display-1" increases rem

    8. Text Alignment & Display
    - block elements spans width. inline does not.
    - d-inline = display inline

    9. Floats & Fixed Positions
    - class="clearfix": Useful for fixing float alignments and spacing. 
    - class="fixed-top": sticks to top of screen

    10. Colors & Background
    - class="invisible" = visibility: hidden;
        - different than display: none; which takes out from DOM, removing spacing.

    11. Margin & Padding Spacing
    - class="mx-5" = margin on x axis
    - class="my-5" = margin on y axis
    - class="b-5" = margin on all sides
    - classes: pt, pb, px: work just like mt, mb, mx but for padding.
    - class="mx-auto" = margin: 0 auto;

    12. Sizing & Borders
    - w and h (25,50,75,100,auto)
        - w-25 = width 25%
        - h-25 = height 25%
    - borders
        - class="border" = simple solid border.
        - class="border-left" = standard left right top bottom.
        - class="border border-primary" = solid border + color
    - rounded borders
        - class="border rounded"
        - class="border rounded-top"
        - class="border rounded-0" = override 



Section 2: Typography & Utilities (59min)

    15. Buttons & Button Groups
    - btn-lg
    - btn-outline-primary
    - btn-primary active = button state pressed
    - btn-primary disabled = button state dimmed out
    - btn-group = on div, attaches buttons side by side.
        - btn-group-vertical
    - btn-toolbar = contains btn-groups making a group of groups.
    -* dropdown (3_2_buttons.html)

    16. Navbar & Navs
    - <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-dark bg-light mt-2 bg-dark">
        - navbar-dark goes with something like bg-dark
    - <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Link 2</a>
        - nav-link active = highlighted link
    - <ul class="mt-5 nav nav-pills nav-fill">
        - nav-fill justifies/spans the ul

    17. List Groups & Badges
    - list-group-flush = no side borders on list



